    <h3>Video Description:</h3>
    <p>
      This video explains the 2025 job market in Saudi Arabia, covering salary ranges for labor, drivers, technicians, office staff, and more. Saudi Arabia remains a top destination due to tax‑free income, safe working culture, and high demand for foreign workers. The video highlights why salaries differ by skills, experience, and city, and also guides new workers on living costs, savings, and how to choose the right job.
    </p>
